@baseUrl = http://localhost:8888
@authToken = your_jwt_token_here
@tariffId = 1

### List all tariffs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tariffs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Configure a new tariff version (ROLE_ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tariffs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meterType": "WATER",
  "consumptionRate": 320.50,
  "fixedServiceCharge": 1000.00,
  "vatRate": 18.0,
  "penaltyRate": 5.0,
  "effectiveFrom": "2026-06-01"
}

### Get a tariff by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tariffs/{{tariffId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### List tariff versions for a meter type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tariffs/type/WATER
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Enable / disable a tariff version
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tariffs/{{tariffId}}/active?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}